body
  .container(style='opacity: 0; transition: opacity .5s;')
    .header(style='padding-bottom: 1.5em')
      ul.nav.nav-pills.pull-right
        li
          a(href='https://github.com/Puffant/puffant-instaprint')
            i.fa.fa-github
            | Source
        li
          a(href='https://github.com/Puffant/puffant-api-doc')
            i.fa.fa-align-center
            | API Document
        li
          a(href='http://www.puffant.com/')
            i.fa.fa-home
            | Puffant

      h3.text-muted 
        i.icon-instagram
        |Puffant instaprint!
    .jumbotron
      h1 这是一个DEMO!
      p.lead
        | Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus.
      p
        a.btn.btn-lg.btn-success(href='/photos/print', role='button') 
          i.fa.fa-print
          |将以下照片发送至Puffant(沙盒)中以打印！
    for row in feed.reduce(reducer_groupBy(4), [])
      .row
        for post in row
          .col-md-3
            .thumbnail(style='margin-bottom: 1em;')
              img(src=post.url_medium, style='width: 100%;')
              .caption(style='height: 2em; overflow: hidden; ')=post.caption
    .footer
      p © Puffant.com 2013
